lead_paragraph: New York Yankees relievers Andrew Miller and Dellin Betances each pitched an inning in their spring training debuts Monday, a 1-0 loss to the Houston Astros.

headline.print_headline: Miller, Betances Make Spring Debuts, Yankees Lose to Astros
